1.title: Spellbound: Crimes of the Mind
1.plot: Sometimes just a tap on the shoulder is enough to put you under a stranger's control. The mystery of mind manipulation, or "pukau" has long since been an enigma. Unravel the secrets behind these crimes of the mind.

2.title: Westall '66: A Suburban Ufo Mystery
2.plot: In 1966, in the Australian suburb of Westall, hundreds of students, teachers, and local residents saw the unimaginable: a UFO. Silenced by authorities at the time, now they revisit the extraordinary experience as a tenacious sleuth searches for answers.

3.title: Vampire Island
3.plot: A crack team of archaeologists and forensic scientists have uncovered hard evidence for the existence of Vampires and the location of mass burial site for the un-dead.

4.title: Vampire Skeletons
4.plot: A new archaeological find reveals a disturbing truth behind the legend of the vampire. Go back hundreds to thousands of years before the creation of our first vampire, Dracula, and look into the darkest depths of humanity's earliest fears of the undead.

5.title: Riddle of the Skies
5.plot: Boldly going where no man has gone before, astronauts, pilots, and scientists are gathered from across the globe to crack the UFO phenomena. From floating lights to objects that defy every law of gravity, unravel the riddle of the skies.

6.title: Halloween: Feast of the Dying Sun
6.plot: We delve into the ancient Celtic origins and the dark fun of Halloween with an eerie journey back in time. Experience the ancient beliefs and practices that are often misconstrued in today's world.

7.title: Exorcism: The Devil Inside
7.plot: The Devil Inside follows the progress of three troubled victims who sought solace through exorcism and explores the impact it has had on their lives. Do Demons truly exist, or are they simply demons of the mind?.

8.title: Confessions of an Alien Abductee
8.plot: Follow the work of one of Britain's most unusual phone-based services, the Anomalous Mind Management Abductee/Contactee Helpline, set up for people who claim to have had close encounters with extraterrestrials.

9.title: My Mum Talks to Aliens
9.plot: Mary Rodwell is a leading authority on extraterrestrial phenomena; her son Chris Rodwell is a vet, a man of science and self-confessed alien skeptic. Their relationship has reached a critical point and something's got to give.

imdb.title: Phenom
plot: Peer into the dark reaches of the human soul. Come face to face with strange beings from other times and other places. _Phenom_ (qv) is an anthology series that will send shivers up your spine and leave you shaking in your boots.
